  %img.scale-with-grid.center{src: "/img/house.jpg"}
  %p We are within easy walking distance of Rosslare Europort, Bus and Rail Stations, local Pubs and Restaurants, and just a twenty minute drive from Wexford town centre.
  %p All bedrooms are spacious and comfortable with an en-suite, TV and tea/coffee making facilities and hair dryer.
  %p Private off-street parking facilities and wireless Broadband are available, and we also provide an early morning breakfast service to accommodate those using the ferry.
