  %h3 A bit about Wexford
  %p There's always something fun to do in Wexford, maybe you can&hellip;
  %ul
    %li
      %strong Go for a swim in our safe, sandy beaches.
      %p Surrounded by miles upon miles beautiful, golden coasts, Rosslare is surrounded by three of Ireland's blue flag beaches:
      %ul.disc
        %li
          %a{href: "http://www.wexford.ie/wex/Departments/Environment/Beaches/RosslareBeach/#d.en.15563"}
            Rosslare Strand
        %li
          %a{href: "http://www.wexford.ie/wex/Departments/Environment/Beaches/MorriscastleBeach/"}
            Morriscastle Beach
        %li
          %a{href: "http://www.wexford.ie/wex/Departments/Environment/Beaches/CurracloeBeach/#d.en.15456"}
            Curracloe Beach
    %li
      %strong Spend a relaxing afternoon fishing.
      %p With dozens of waterways and hundreds of kilometres of coasts, you're never far from a good fishing spot in County Wexford. There is a map of some of these locations <a href="http://goo.gl/maps/HsmgV">here</a> for your convenience.
    %li
      %strong Play a round of golf.
      %p Wexford is home to many of the countries <a href="http://www.visitwexford.ie/index.php?contentid=golf">finest golf courses</a>, including several championship courses.
    %li
      %strong Find a little excitement?
      %p Maybe go horse-riding at the local stables, rent a boat and visit the islands, or go on an adventure in one of Wexford's adventure parks. You can even go kite-surfing just up the road in Hooked Kite Surfing on Duncannon beach.
    %li
      %strong Take in some of our history.
      %p Visit the Irish National Heritage Park, walk around Johnstown Castle and its beautiful grounds or see what life was like for Irish emigrants aboard the Dunbrody Famine Ship in New Ross.
  %hr/
.one-third.column
  .sticky
    %h3
      Make an enquiry.
    %form{action: "/contact", method: "post", id: "contactForm"}
      %label{for: "name"}
        Name
      %input{type: "text", name: "name", required: "", id: "name"}
      
      %label{for: "email"}
        Email address
      %input{type: "email", name: "email", required: "", id: "email"}

      %label{for: "comment"}
        Details of your visit.
      %span.sub When will you arrive? How long do you plan to stay? Do you have any requirements or questions?
      %textarea{name: "comment", required: "", id: "comment"}

      %button.full-width{type: "submit"}
        Submit.
